00:22:57,156 --> 00:23:01,308
Sister Rosa,
would you mind?

244
00:23:22,181 --> 00:23:25,332
Cody fixed the bird!
Cody fixed the bird!

245
00:23:25,184 --> 00:23:28,335
Maybe he was just knocked out
when he hit the window.

246
00:23:28,187 --> 00:23:30,337
No, he was dead.

247
00:23:30,189 --> 00:23:34,341
[ All ] Cody fixed the bird!
Cody fixed the bird!

248
00:23:34,193 --> 00:23:38,345
