She's special. You know that,
don't you? That's why they want her.

282
00:26:06,345 --> 00:26:09,496
Please tell me
where my sister is.

283
00:26:09,348 --> 00:26:13,500
Forget about your sister, okay?
They've already got her.

284
00:26:13,352 --> 00:26:15,502
Don't let them get
the little girl.

285
00:26:15,354 --> 00:26:19,506
- [Door Opens]
- Maggie, I need you in four.

286
00:26:19,358 --> 00:26:21,508
- Doctor--
- Right now!

287
00:26:21,360 --> 00:26:25,512
Stay here.

288
00:26:32,371 --> 00:26:35,522
Task force hot line.
Can I help you?

289
00:26:35,374 --> 00:26:36,523
Please, ma'am, slow down.

290
00:26:36,375 --> 00:26:39,526
What makes you think that
your landlord is the killer?

291
00:26:39,378 --> 00:26:42,529
[Chatter Continues,
Indistinct]

292
00:26:42,381 --> 00:26:43,530
Crawford, I hate to break it
to you,

293
00:26:43,382 --> 00:26:47,534
but that weed's been dead
for at least two weeks.

294
00:26:49,388 --> 00:26:52,539
Excuse me.

295
00:26:52,391 --> 00:26:55,542
- What is that?
