and familiar faces.

454
00:38:51,109 --> 00:38:53,259
Then the sooner she gets
familiar with us, the better.

455
00:38:53,111 --> 00:38:57,263
- [Knock On Door]
- Ah, Dahnia.

456
00:38:58,116 --> 00:39:01,267
This is Dahnia, Mags.
She's wonderful with children.

457
00:39:01,119 --> 00:39:04,270
Hello, Miss O'Connor.
May I see the child?

458
00:39:04,122 --> 00:39:08,274
- No, you can't.
- As you wish.

459
00:39:09,127 --> 00:39:13,279
Maggie, really there's
no reason to beso defensive.

460
00:39:13,131 --> 00:39:17,283
We want you to be part of the family
and visit Cody regularly.

461
00:39:17,135 --> 00:39:21,287
This is crazy. It's too soon.
I have to talk to Cody.

462
00:39:22,140 --> 00:39:26,292
- No. There's nothing to talk about.
-Jenna, please.

463
00:39:26,144 --> 00:39:29,295
Well, I think
this visit is over.

464
00:39:29,147 --> 00:39:33,299
Jenna, why don't you
wait in the car?

465
00:39:38,156 --> 00:39:42,308
Maggie, I want you to think
this through carefully.

466
00:39:42,160 --> 00:39:45,311
Jenna and l, we only
want what's best for Cody.

467
00:39:45,163 --> 00:39:49,315
You don't know her yet. She doesn't
know you. This will take time.

468
00:39:49,167 --> 00:39:51,317
I'm afraid you don't
have that luxury.

469
00:39:51,169 --> 00:39:54,320
You're gonna have to decide
right now, today,

470
00:39:54,172 --> 00:39:56,322
how you're going to deal with this.

471
00:39:56,174 --> 00:40:00,326
And I promise you, you do not
want this in some court's hands...

472
00:40:00,178 --> 00:40:04,330
for your own good--
and for Cody's.

473
00:40:05,183 --> 00:40:09,335
Good-bye, Maggie.

474
00:40:13,191 --> 00:40:17,343
- Cody?
- [Cartoon On TV]

475
00:40:18,196 --> 00:40:22,348
Cody?

476
00:40:23,201 --> 00:40:27,353
Cody.

477
00:40:29,207 --> 00:40:32,358
[Hissing, Whispering,
Indistinct]

478
00:40:32,210 --> 00:40:36,362
Cody!

479
00:40:38,216 --> 00:40:42,368
[Tires Screeching]

480
00:40:43,221 --> 00:40:47,373
No!

481
00:40:51,229 --> 00:40:54,380
- He grabbed her out of my bedroom!
- Calm down.

482
00:40:54,232 --> 00:40:58,384
No, I won't calm down. I won't
leave here until somebody helps me.

483
00:40:58,236 --> 00:40:59,385
